data.description: Seller is motivated as he wants to relocate. Come make an offer. Great home with huge shop and pool. Country setting yet close to anything you would need. This corner lot makes it an easy drive to Springfield or Buffalo. Spacious living area with gas fire place. Home even hosts a bar and game room area. Shop has a car lift, wood burning stove, office and or living quarters area, full bath room, and is very well insulated. Shop is even on its own septic tank. The 6.69 m/l acres includes big yard, pond, and some woods which would be great for horses or a few animals. Shop has 2 bays with door openers. Detached 2 car garage with door opener. There are also 2 carports, 2 storage buildings, and a cook shack. What else do you need!?!
